profile:
As your family grows, you may find your home doesn’t quite meet your needs. It may be lacking in space or have an outdated layout. Moving, however, might not be the best option. After all, it can be difficult finding a new house on the market that meets your criteria while also staying within budget. Instead of giving up on your current home, why not renovate? Home renovation in Saskatoon is a great way to get the most out of your home investment without breaking the budget. At Lekadez Services, we specialize in professional home and commercial renovation. We renovate basements, update kitchens, install tile floors, paint, repair windows, and much more.

Why Hire a Professional for Renovation Project?
We get it, a do-it-yourself project looks tempting. After all, if you’re planning to do an extensive renovation instead of looking for a new home in order to save money, you may think to do the project yourself is just another way to stay within budget. However, if you are new to renovating or don’t have enough free time to devote to the project, your inexperience and busy schedule may end up costing you more in the long run. A professional will be able to plan accordingly, purchasing the exact tools and materials needed for the job and avoiding unnecessary costs. Professionals also have a dedicated team to work on the project, tackling the job so it gets done as quickly and efficiently as possible.

Request a Free Estimate
Start planning your renovation project. Contact Lekadez Services for a free estimate.
payment_method: E-transfer, cash, cheque, credit and Debit Card!
project_minimum: No job is too small or big
